st%20man%20is%20an%20American.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsn't%20it%20necessary%20for%20your%20eldest%20American%20son%20to%20withdraw%20his%20citizenship%3F%26quot%3B%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F1771474495%2FO4lVnccRg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChinese%20blogger%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESome%20think%20Nongfu%20Spring%20loves%20Japan%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hostility%20escalated%20this%20week%20into%20claims%20that%20Nongfu%20Spring%20was%20intentionally%20planting%20elements%20of%20Japanese%20culture%20into%20its%20product%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%20is%20strongly%20disliked%20by%20Chinese%20nationalists%2C%20linked%20in%20particular%20to%20atrocities%20committed%20during%20World%20War%20II%20and%20the%20country's%20refusal%20to%20acknowledge%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommentators%20on%20Weibo%2C%20China's%20version%20of%20X%2C%20took%20issue%20with%20a%20pagoda%20on%20the%20design%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F6478526806%2FO3EPtgOKy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENongfu%20Spring's%20green%20tea%20bottle%20label%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20it%20resembled%20the%20Sensoji%20Temple%20in%20Tokyo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20blasted%20the%20label%20of%20another%20beverage%20that%20featured%20carp%20streamers%2C%20which%20are%20known%20as%20Koinobori%20in%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20longtime%20design%20of%20Nongfu%20Spring's%20signature%20bottled%20water%20came%20under%20fire%2C%20with%20some%20users%20saying%20a%20mountain%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F6120606636%2FO3NSzve1X%3Frefer_flag%3D1001030103_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elogo%20closely%20resembled%20Japan's%20Mount%20Fuji.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20online%20think%20Nongfu%20Spring's%20logo%20looks%20like%20Mount%20Fuji.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f40c6b3037f8e81750add6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeople%20online%20think%20Nongfu%20Spring's%20logo%20looks%20like%20Mount%20Fuji.%3Cp%3ECFOTO%2FFuture%20Publishing%20via%20Getty%20Images%20and%20Jinhee%20Lee%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20complaint%20accused%20Nongfu%20Spring%20of%20using%20a%20red%20bottle%20cap%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F39297060%2FO4ejVpoQq%3Frefer_flag%3D1001030103_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresembles%20the%20Japanese%20flag.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20March%203%2C%20Zhong%20posted%20a%20response%20to%20the%20backlash%20via%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2FrPyxHJD7esq07DCFbtQWXg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENongfu%20Spring's%20WeChat%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20his%20relationship%20with%20Zong%20was%20marked%20by%20mutual%20respect%20and%20warmth%20despite%20past%20legal%20disputes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Zong%20hated%20online%20violence%20during%20his%20lifetime.%20I%20never%20thought%20that%20after%20Mr%20Zong%20passed%20away%2C%20there%20would%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20online%20slander%20against%20me%20and%20Nongfu%20Spring%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20definitely%20not%20what%20Mr%20Zong%20wanted%20to%20see.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhong%20added%20that%20he%20hoped%20people%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20be%20swayed%20by%20individual%20self-media%20or%20influencers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globaltimes.cn%2Fpage%2F202403%2F1308453.shtml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Global%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Chinese%20media%20outlet%20known%20for%20promoting%20the%20ruling%20party's%20views%2C%20also%20reported%20on%20March%208%20that%20Nongfu%20Spring%20said%20the%20design%20of%20its%20green%20tea%20bottle%20was%20based%20on%20a%20Chinese%20temple%2C%20not%20a%20Japanese%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20nationalist%20movem