income%20with%20insufficient%20affordable%20housing%20available.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20competitive%20rental%20markets%20in%20the%20country%20are%20failing%20to%20add%20enough%20new%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20according%20to%20a%20new%20analysis%20of%20the%20country's%20139%20largest%20rental%20markets%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rentcafe.com%2Fblog%2Frental-market%2Frental-competitiveness-index%2Fus-hottest-rental-markets-start-of-2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eby%20RentCafe%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20found%20that%2017%20of%20the%2020%20most%20competitive%20rental%20markets%20in%20the%20US%20are%20building%20less%20than%20the%20national%20average.%20Four%20of%20these%20markets%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Oklahoma%20City%2C%20the%20Bridgeport-New%20Haven%20area%20in%20Connecticut%2C%20the%20Lansing-Ann%20Arbor%2C%20Michigan%20area%2C%20and%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20California%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0added%20virtually%20no%20new%20apartments%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20share%20of%20newly%20constructed%20apartments%20in%20rental%20markets%20across%20the%20country%20is%200.67%25.%20Brooklyn%2C%20New%20York%2C%20had%20just%200.19%25%20at%20the%20start%20of%202024%2C%20San%20Diego%20had%20just%200.24%25%2C%20and%20North%20New%20Jersey%20had%20just%200.51%25%2C%20RentCafe%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20determined%20market%20competitiveness%20using%20five%20factors%2C%20including%20the%20percentage%20of%20apartments%20occupied%20by%20tenants%2C%20the%20number%20of%20days%20it%20takes%20to%20fill%20an%20apartment%2C%20and%20the%20share%20of%20newly%20constructed%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20change%20over%20the%20last%20year%20in%20most%20markets%20was%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20days%20a%20typical%20apartment%20sits%20unoccupied%20in%20between%20tenants%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0jumping%20from%2038%20days%20in%20early%202023%20to%2041%20days%20in%20early%202024%2C%20RentCafe%20found.%