ovement%20you%20enjoy%20can%20help%20you%20get%20fitter%20and%20live%20longer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EYou'll%20know%20your%20workouts%20are%20effective%20if%20you%20notice%20they%20feel%20easier%20or%20you%20can%20do%20more%20over%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EExercising%20regularly%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20keep%20your%20heart%20healthy%20and%20stave%20off%20aging%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20spend%20hours%20a%20week%20to%20benefit%2C%20according%20to%20a%20cardiologist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20cutting-edge%20wearables%20and%20advances%20in%20the%20booming%20fitness%20tech%20industry%2C%20it's%20easier%20than%20ever%20to%20keep%20tabs%20on%20your%20heart%20health%20in%20real%20time.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvo2-max-explained-what-is-good-how-improve-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFitness%20stats%20like%20VO2%20max%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20help%20make%20sure%20you're%20getting%20the%20most%20out%20of%20your%20exercise%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20with%20all%20the%20data%20available%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20overcomplicate%20your%20workouts%2C%20said%20Dr.%20Edo%20Paz%2C%20a%20cardiologist%20at%20White%20Plains%20Hospital%20and%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20medical%20affairs%20at%20the%20digital%20health%20company%20Hello%20Heart.%20While%20it%20can%20be%20motivating%20to%20measure%20your%20health%20progress%20with%20metrics%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgood-resting-heart-rate-how-to-know-improve-longevity-fitness-2024-3%3Fmrfhud%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresting%20heart%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20real%20test%20is%20low-tech%2C%20Paz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20people%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20any%20of%20this%20stuff.%20You%20just%20need%20to%20go%20out%20and%20start%20doing%20some%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAn%20easy%20way%20to%20test%20your%20heart%20health%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECan%20you%20climb%20more%20flights%20of%20stairs%20without%20getting%20out%20of%20breath%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20simple%20measurement%20of%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrain-for-fitness-level-maximize-muscle-gains-trainer-advice-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efitness%20level%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Maybe%20you%20used%20to%20get%20winded%20after%20walking%20just%20three%20blocks%20with%20your%20dog%20but%20now%20do%20five%20or%20more%20without%20breaking%20a%20sweat.%20That's%20a%20good%20sign%20you're%20getting%20fit%2C%20which%20means%20a%20healthier%2C%20more%20efficient%20heart%20and%20better%20odds%20of%20living%20longer%2C%20Paz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20understand%20your%20current%20fitness%20level%20and%20heart%20health%2C%20you%20can%20set%20yourself%20small%2C%20achievable%20goals%2C%20then%20try%20the%20test%20again%20and%20see%20exactly%20how%20much%20you've%20improved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20understand%20that%20if%20they%20can%20do%20more%2C%20that%20means%20that%20they're%20more%20fit%2C%26quot%3B%20Paz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EJust%20a%20few%20extra%20minutes%20of%20exercise%20a%20day%20adds%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20fitness%20mistakes%20you%20can%20make%20for%20your%20health%20is%20taking%20on%20too%20much%20too%20fast%2C%20according%20to%20Paz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20start%20small%20and%20build%20on%20it.%20You%20don't%20need%20to%20run%20a%20marathon%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStart%20by%20figuring%20out%20how%20much%20exercise%20you%20typically%20get%20in%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20guidelines%20recommend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexercise-weekend-can-lower-risk-early-death-study-finds-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E150%20minutes%20per%20week%20of%20moderate-intensity%20exercise%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20you're%20working%20just%20hard%20enough%20that%20you%20can't%20carry%20a%20conversation%2C%2075%20minutes%20of%20vigorous%20activity%2C%20at%20a%20pace%20that%20leaves%20you%20out%20of%20breath%2C%20or%20a%20combination%20of%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaz%20said%20if%20you're%20not%20there%20yet%2C%20adding%20a%20little%20more%20exercise%20at%20a%20time%20can%20make%20a%20big%20difference%2C%20with%20an%20extra%2010%20minutes%20a%20day%20as%20a%20good%20starting%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20important%20to%20break%20it%20down%20into%20more%20bite-sized%2C%20achievable%20things%20so%20that%20you%20can%20gain%20some%20success%20and%20build%20on%20that.%20Even%2010%20minutes%20is%20meaningful%20and%20will%20make%20a%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BJust%20because%20you're%20not%20at%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20a%20week%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20it's%20not%20worthwhile.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20don't%20have%20to%20run%20or%20jog%20to%20boost%20your%20heart%20health%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20hate%20running%20or%20struggle%20to%20find%20time%20for%20the%20gym%2C%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20more%20accessible%20activities%20to%20help%20you%20hit%20your%20exercise%20goals%2C%20according%20to%20Paz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20adding%20a%20little%20more%20physical%20activity%20to%20your%20day%20is%20key%2C%20whether%20that's%20going%20for%20a%20short%20walk%2C%20playing%20sports%2C%20or%20taking%20the%20stairs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20an%20activity%20you%20enjoy%20and%20can%20realistically%20do%20can%20help%20you%20be%20more%20consistent%20with%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20just%20need%20to%20be%20jogging%2C%20it%20doesn't%20need%20to%20be%20elliptical%20or%20cycling.%20If%20you%20like%20dancing%2C%20if%20you%20like%20pickleball%2C%20if%20you%20like%20basketball%2C%20if%20you%20like%20playing%20tag%20