20Academy%20in%20Cochin%2C%20commanding%20INS%20Beas%20which%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20during%20the%201971%20India-Pakistan%20war%2C%20serving%20as%20the%20Indian%20Naval%20Attache%20in%20Bonn%2C%20West%20Germany%20(1973-76)%2C%20serving%20as%20Fleet%20Commander%20of%20the%20Eastern%20Naval%20Command%2C%20and%20commanding%20both%20the%20Southern%20and%20Eastern%20Naval%20Commands.%20He%20took%20over%20as%20the%2013th%20Chief%20of%20Naval%20Staff%20(CNS)%20on%2030th%20November%201990%20and%20retired%20from%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20in%201993.%20It%20was%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20CNS%20that%20women%20were%20inducted%20into%20the%20armed%20forces%20with%20the%20Navy%20showing%20the%20lead.%C2%A0%20This%20was%20in%20keeping%20with%20his%20lifelong%20commitment%20to%20gender%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20retirement%2C%20Admiral%20Ramdas%20settled%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Bhaimala%2C%20Alibag%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20on%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20awarded%20to%20him%20by%20the%20government%20of%20Maharashtra%20in%20recognition%20of%20his%20acts%20of%20gallantry%20in%20the%201971%20war%20operations.%20Here%2C%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20Lalita%20Ramdas%20developed%20and%20planted%20diverse%C2%A0%20trees%2C%20practiced%20organic%20farming%2C%20and%20involved%20themselves%20in%20a%20range%20of%20public%20service%20activities.%20These%20included%20being%20actively%20involved%20in%20the%20Pakistan%20India%20People%E2%80%99s%20Forum%20for%20Peace%20and%20Democracy%20(PIPPFD)%2C%20Indo-Pakistan%20Soldiers%20Initiative%C2%A0%20for%20Peace%20(IPSI)%2C%20the%20anti-nuclear%20peace%20movement%20-Coalition%20for%20Nuclear%20Disarmament%20and%20Peace%20(CNDP)%2C%C2%A0%20supporting%20the%20struggle%20against%20an%20SEZ%20under%20the%20%3Cem%3E22%20Gaon%20Bachao%20Andolan%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Raigad%20district%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20movement%20for%20gender%20equality%2C%C2%A0%20fisherpeople%E2%80%99s%20rights%2C%20the%20rights%20of%20farmers%2C%20the%20rights%20of%20religious%20and%20ethnic%20minorities%2C%20and%20many%20others.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20he%20became%20an%20outspoken%20voice%20of%20conscience%2C%20advocating%20actively%20for%20the%20defence%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%2C%20especially%20the%20values%20of%20liberty%2C%20equality%2C%20fraternity%20and%20secularism.%20He%20was%20particularly%20concerned%20about%20maintaining%20secularism%20and%20the%20commitment%20to%20constitutional%20values%20among%20the%20Indian%20Armed%20Forces.%C2%A0%20He%20reminded%20them%20of%20their%20oath%20to%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%20He%20continuously%20advocated%20with%C2%A0%20political%20parties%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20these%20same%20core%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20fearlessly%20voiced%20his%20opinions%20about%20injustices%20against%20marginalised%20and%20minority%20communities%20and%20wrote%20several%20representations%20to%20the%20highest%20authorities%2C%20condemning%20the%20communalisation%20and%20polarisation%20being%20promoted%2C%20and%20urged%20them%20to%20uphold%20democracy%20and%20the%20secular%20fabric%20of%C2%A0%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710494458000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F15144956%2FGIsGrdcW0AAoSLg.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fex-naval-chief-admiral-laxminarayan-ramdas-passes-away-at-95%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20the%20years%2C%20Admiral%20Ramdas%20became%20an%20outspoken%20voice%20of%20conscience%2C%20advocating%20actively%20for%20the%20defence%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%2C%20especially%20the%20values%20of%20liberty%2C%20equality%2C%20fraternity%20and%20secularism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fex-naval-chief-admiral-laxminarayan-ramdas-passes-away-at-95%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Feb%20trade%20deficit%20at%20%2418.71%20billion%2C