ref%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeta-cofounder-send-elon-musk-part-heart-when-she-dies-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%20for%20the%20Ethical%20Treatment%20of%20Animals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20PETA%2C%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY1NZRAZM12Q%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestigative%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20posted%20on%20YouTube%20on%20March%205%20that%20tourists%20should%20be%20wary%20of%20drinking%20kopi%20luwak%2C%20as%20the%20coffee%20beans%20are%20collected%20from%20civets%20kept%20in%20wire%20cages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20comprised%20footage%20of%20several%20civets%20held%20in%20captivity.%20Jason%20Baker%2C%20the%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20PETA%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F03%2F08%2Fwhat-is-civet-coffee-peta-issues-a-new-warning-to-bali-tourists.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCNBC%2520Travel-%2CA%2520new%2520warning%2520to%2520Bali%2520tourists%253A%2520%2527Stay%2520away%2Cfrom%2520civet%2520coffee%252C%2527%2520says%2520PETA%26amp%3Btext%3DIf%2520the%2520idea%2520of%2520drinking%2Creason%2520to%2520rethink%2520the%2520drink.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20footage%20was%20taken%20at%20a%20farm%20in%20Catur%2C%20a%20small%20town%2030%20miles%20north%20of%20Ubud%20that's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epopular%20for%20trekking%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbali-digital-nomad-cost-jobs-career-guide-lifestyle-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBali%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20one%20person%20could%20be%20heard%20saying%20the%20coffee%20beans%20are%20collected%20from%20the%20civet%20droppings%20found%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bwild%20jungle%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20but%20PETA%20wrote%20in%20the%20video%20that%20this%20isn't%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeliberately%20misleading%20claims%20about%20how%20civet%20coffee%20is%20obtained%20are%20rampant%20in%20Bali%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20video's%20in-text%20caption%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20person%2C%20whom%20PETA%20identified%20as%20a%20kopi%20luwak%20peddler%2C%20said%20that%20tourists%20don't%20know%20that%20the%20civets%20are%20held%20captive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20because%20we%20forcibly%20%5Bconfine%5D%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20person%20said%20in%20response%20to%20the%20investigator%20asking%20if%20kopi%20luwak%20is%20better%20than%20regular%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20ends%20with%20the%20in-text%20caption%3A%20%26quot%3BDon't%20be%20fooled.%20There%20is%20no%20ethically%20made%20civet%20coffee.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaker%20told%20CNBC%20that%20it's%20not%20possible%20to%20produce%20kopi%20luwak%20in%20mass%20quantities%20without%20caging%20civets.%20He%20said%20civets%20were%20also%20found%20to%20have%20been%20fed%20rotten%20coffee%20berries%2C%20covered%20in%20feces%2C%20and%20had%20open%20wounds.%20The%20Bali%20Tourism%20Board%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20regarding%20its%20regulations%20on%20producing%20and%20selling%20kopi%20luwak%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20confinement%2C%20suffering%2C%20and%20sadness%20endured%20by%C2%A0civet%C2%A0cats%20for%20kopi%20luwak%20aren't%20among%20them.%C2%A0Tourists%20be%20warned%3A%20stay%20away%20from%C2%A0civet%C2%A0coffee%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20PETA%20and%20Baker%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKopi%20luwak%20is%20made%20by%20cleaning%20and%20roasting%20partially%20digested%20coffee%20beans%20excreted%20by%20civets.%20Kopi%20luwak%20is%20also%20known%20for%20its%20high%20price%20point%2C%20costing%20between%20%2445%20and%20%24600%20per%20pound%2C%20Baker%20told%20CNBC.%20It's%20big%20business%20%E2%80%94%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20Ohio-based%20research%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C