ebsite%20of%20a%20company%20that%20I%20hadn't%20heard%20of%20but%20that%20several%20popular%20review%20sites%20recommended.%20I%20lingered%20on%20the%20product%20page%20for%20several%20minutes%2C%20reading%20the%20specifications%20of%20the%20topper%20and%20comparing%20it%20with%20other%20options.%20Then%20I%20closed%20the%20window%20and%20went%20on%20with%20my%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20an%20hour%20or%20so%20later%2C%20an%20email%20appeared%20in%20my%20inbox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThanks%20for%20stopping%20by!%26quot%3B%20the%20subject%20line%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20body%20of%20the%20email%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWelcome!%26quot%3B%20and%20offered%20me%20a%20discount%20on%20toppers%2C%20pillows%2C%20and%20bedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20perplexed.%20I%20hadn't%20purchased%20anything.%20I%20hadn't%20submitted%20my%20information%20in%20a%20pop-up%20box%20for%20a%20discount.%20How%20did%20the%20company%20get%20my%20email%3F%20The%20confusion%20quickly%20gave%20way%20to%20annoyance%20and%20discomfort.%20Even%20if%20they%20somehow%20had%20my%20email%2C%20why%20were%20they%20cold-emailing%20me%20uninvited%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData-privacy%20experts%20I%20spoke%20with%20were%20not%20surprised%20to%20hear%20this%20story.%20Despite%20the%20sense%20of%20anonymity%20that%20comes%20with%20online%20browsing%2C%20the%20websites%20you%20visit%20know%20exactly%20who%20you%20are%20more%20often%20than%20you'd%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWelcome%20to%20the%20internet%20of%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Rob%20Shavell%2C%20a%20cofounder%20and%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20online-privacy%20companies%20Abine%20and%20DeleteMe%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20just%20happen%20to%20you%3B%20it%20happens%20to%20millions%20of%20people%20every%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvasion-of-data-privacy-online-in-person-examples-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EData%20brokers%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20amassing%20more%20and%20more%20information%20about%20individuals%20every%20day%2C%20compiling%20it%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-cook-apple-blasted-data-brokers-privacy-time-magazine-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprofiles%20that%20they%20then%20sell%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20companies%20or%20even%20individuals.%20Shavell%20said%20when%20DeleteMe%20started%20measuring%20this%20about%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20average%20profile%20from%20a%20data%20broker%20contained%20235%20pieces%20of%20personal%2C%20identifiable%20information%20about%20a%20person.%20Today%2C%20it's%20over%20600.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20five%20years%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20information%20that%20the%20average%20data%20broker%20has%20on%20the%20average%20person's%20profile%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20information%20can%20include%20where%20you%20live%2C%20who%20your%20family%20members%20are%2C%20what%20political%20party%20you're%20associated%20with%2C%20and%20what%20kind%20of%20car%20you%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20companies%20that%20do%20%26quot%3Benrichment%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20Shavell%20described%20as%20an%20industry%20term%20for%20the%20practice%20of%20knowing%20one%20thing%20about%20somebody%20and%20then%20using%20it%20to%20correlate%20other%20information%20that%20is%20known%20about%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20offered%20a%20possible%20explanation%20of%20what%20happened%20in%20my%20case%3A%20When%20I%20visited%20the%20website%2C%20it%20gathered%20some%20pieces%20of%20unique%20data%20from%20me%2C%20like%20my%20IP%20address%20combined%20with%20the%20fonts%20on%20my%20device%20or%20the%20International%20Mobile%20Equipment%20Identity%20number%20on%20my%20cellphone.%20It%20then%20shot%20the%20data%20it%20collected%20over%20to%20a%20data-enrichment%20broker%2C%20which%20determined%20with%2C%20say%2C%2093%25%20confidence%20that%20this%20is%20Kelsey%20Vlamis%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBy%20the%20way%2C%20we%20know%20all%20of%20this%20stuff%20about%20her.%20What%20do%20you%20want%20to%20know%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20can%20then%20pay%20for%20whatever%20it%20wants%20to%20know%20about%20you%2C%20such%20as%20your%20email%20address%20and%20maybe%20even%20some%20other%20information%20that%20it%20can%20use%20to%20do%20a%20follow-up%20campaign%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20automatically%20all%20happens%2C%20and%20the%20transactions%20all%20get%20done%2C%20and%20you%20get%20an%20uncomfortably%20personalized%20email%20based%20on%20an%20action%20you%20took%20when%20you%20thought%20you%20were%20more%20or%20less%20anonymous%2C%26quot%3B%20Shavell%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20happening%20all%20over%20the%20internet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIf%20websites%20know%20who%20I%20am%2C%20why%20don't%20I%20get%20more%20unsolicited%20emails%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20explanation%20made%20sense%2C%20but%20it%20did%20make%20me%20wonder%20why%20I%20hadn't%20heard%20of%20this%20happening%20more%20often%2C%20especially%20because%20Shavell's%20educated%20guess%20was%20that%20in%20the%20US%2C%20slightly%20more%20than%20half%20of%20all%20people's%20browsing%20could%20be%20identified%20by%20marketers%20or%20data%20brokers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Shavell%20said%20one%20of%20the%20big%20secrets%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcars-recording-data-onstar-gm-lexisnexis-insurance-rates-increase-report-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata-broker%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20marketing-technology%20industry%20was%20its%20efforts%20to%20actively%20avoid%20creating%20the%20situation%20I%20experienced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20know%20more%20and%20more%20about%20you%20but%20not%20creep%20you%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20actually%20typically%20don't%20do%20this.%20This%20is%20probably%20just%20sloppy%20marketing%20that%20you%20ran%20into.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20companies%20are%20usually%20gathering%20my%20data%20without%20showing%20me%20their%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDominic%20Sellitto%2C%20a%20clinical%20assistant%20professor%20of%20management%20science%20and%20systems%20at%20the%20University%20at%20Buffalo%20School%20of%20Management%2C%20calls%20it%20the%20%26quot%3Bcreep%20factor%26quot%3B%20of%20using%20someone's%20data.%20He%20told%20BI%20most%20companies%20would%20not%20use%20a%20person's%20data%20in%20this%20way%20specifically%20because%20they%20know%20it%20can%20creep%20people%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20certain%20point%20at%20which%2C%20and%20I'm%20sure%20it%20sounds%20like%20you've%20encountered%20it%2C%20where%20I%20don't%20like%20that%20they%20sent%20me%20an%20email%20unsolicited%2C%20and%20therefore%20I%20am%20less%20likely%20to%20purchase%20something%20from%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20companies%20will%20tend%20to%20avoid%20crossing%20that%20boundary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20situation%20like%20what%20happened%20to%20me%2C%20Sellitto%20said%2C%20it's%20more%20often%20the%20case%20that%20the%20company%20appearing%20to%20have%20cold-emailed%20you%20is%20affiliated%20with%20a%20company%20that%20you%20have%20given%20your%20data%20to%20%E2%80%94%20for%20instance%2C%20if%20you%20buy%20from%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20a%20bigger%20company%20or%20a%20sister%20brand%20to%20a%20company%20you%20have%20shopped%20at.%20However%2C%20in%20my%20case%2C%20I%20could%20find%20no%20evidence%20of%20a%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20options%20for%20people%20who%20are%20concerned%20about%20their%20personal%20data%20being%20out%20there.%20Some%20states%2C%20including%20California%2C%20Colorado%2C%20Connecticut%2C%20Virginia%2C%20and%20Utah%2C%20have%20passed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncsl.org%2Ftechnology-and-communication%2Fstate-laws-related-to-digital-privacy%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFive%2520states%E2%80%94California%252C%2520Colorado%252C%2Cof%2520personal%2520information%252C%2520among%2520others.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata-privacy%20laws%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20give%20residents%20the%20right%20to%20have%20their%20personal%20data%20deleted%20or%20prevent%20it%20from%20being%20sold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fincogni-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehundreds%20of%20data%20brokers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20they%20all%20have%20different%20processes%20for%20opting%20out.%20If%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20go%20through%20the%20process%20of%20requesting%20data%20deletion%20from%20individual%20data%20brokers%2C%20you%20can%20pay%20for%20services%20such%20as%20DeleteMe%20or%20Incogni%2C%20which%20can%20send%20requests%20to%20brokers%20on%20your%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20my%20case%20was%20innocuous%2C%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20circumstances%20in%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplanned-parenthood-abortion-clinic-data-broker-sale-report-says-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprivate%20data%20can%20be%20used%20that%20are%20far%20more%20malicious%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Shavell%20said%20situations%20like%20this%20could%20help%20open%20people's%20eyes%20to%20just%20how%20accessible%20their%20personal%20information%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20don't%20want%20to%20have%20happen%20is%20five%20years%20from%20now%2C%20nobody's%20done%20anything%20about%20their%20privacy%2C%20and%20then%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20AI%20algorithms%20have%20collected%20so%20much%20data%20about%20us%20they're%20making%20decisions%20that%20impact%20our%20lives%20behind%20our%20back%2C%20so%20to%20speak%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20never%20know%20about%20it%2C%20and%20we%20feel%20a%20real%20loss%20of%20control.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20news%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Akv