he%20state%20BJP%20president%2C%20Manmohan%20Samal%2C%20caused%20a%20stir%20on%20Thursday%20(March%2014)%20with%20his%20fluctuating%20stance%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20his%20return%20from%20Delhi%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Samal%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20form%20the%20government%20alone%20in%20the%20state%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fspeculation-alliance-bjd-odisha-bjp-chief-form-govt-evades-tie-up-9213985%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EOdia%20asmita%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Odia%20pride)%20will%20be%20our%20primary%20electoral%20focus%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20later%20changed%20his%20stance%20and%20removed%20his%20statement%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20which%20suggested%20the%20BJP%20would%20solely%20govern%20Odisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhatever%20I%20said%20is%20my%20personal%20opinion%20and%20there%20should%20not%20be%20any%20interpretation%20of%20my%20words.%20I%20have%20not%20said%20a%20single%20word%20on%20alliance.%20Any%20decision%20(on%20alliance)%20will%20be%20taken%20by%20our%20national%20president%20and%20parliamentary%20board%20and%20that%20will%20be%20final%20and%20we%20will%20obey%20them.%20We%20are%20working%20in%20all%2021%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20and%20147%20assembly%20seats%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Samal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlliance%20talks%20gained%20momentum%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fodisha-bjp-bjd-alliance%5C%22%3Evisited%3C%2Fa%3E%20Odisha%20on%20March%205.%20During%20the%20visit%2C%20he%20was%20seen%20holding%20chief%20minister%20Naveen%20Patnaik%E2%80%99s%20hand%20and%20exchanging%20pleasantries%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20the%20state%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20who%20visited%20Delhi%20thrice%20over%20the%20last%20fortnight%2C%20held%20a%20series%20of%20discussions%20with%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20central%20leaders%2C%20including%20with%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20Wednesday%20evening%2C%20where%20they%20tried%20to%20argue%20against%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20leadership%20is%20learnt%20to%20have%20told%20the%20central%20leaders%20that%20the%20party%20would%20%E2%80%9Close%20credibility%E2%80%9D%20if%20it%20aligned%20with%20the%20BJD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBJP%20has%20been%20opposing%20the%20BJD%20ever%20since%20the%20regional%20party%20unilaterally%20severed%20ties%20in%202009%20after%2011%20years%20of%20alliance.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20fighting%20against%20the%20BJD.%20After%20Narendra%20Modi%20became%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20people%20have%20started%20looking%20at%20the%20BJP%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20BJD%2C%20and%20made%20the%20party%20the%20main%20Opposition%20party%20in%20Odisha%20in%202019.%20Our%20workers%20have%20undergone%20torture%20over%20the%20years%2C%20some%20have%20even%20sacrificed%20their%20lives.%20We%20have%20apprised%20the%20central%20leaders%20about%20these%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20BJP%20leader%2C%20requesting%20anonymity%2C%20told%20the%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20stated%20that%20Shah%20assured%20he%20would%20communicate%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20state%20leadership%20to%20Modi%2C%20emphasising%20that%20the%20final%20decision%20would%20rest%20with%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20according%20to%20BJD%20sources%20cited%20by%20the%20newspaper%2C%20there%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20general%20consensus%20within%20the%20party%20regarding%20an%20alliance.%20However%2C%20the%20party%20has%20expressed%20concerns%20over%20seat-sharing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20not%20be%20correct%20to%20brush%20aside%20the%20possibility%20of%20an%20alliance.%20The%20ball%20is%20in%20the%20courts%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Naveen%20Patnaik.%20They%20will%20take%20a%20call%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20BJD%20leader%20told%20the%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710491457000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08091041%2FGH6wRL5W4AAQK0I.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fodisha-bjp-presidents-flip-flop-on-alliance-with-bjd-sparks-uncertainty-ahead-of-polls%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alliance%20talks%20gained%20momentum%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20visited%20Odisha%20on%20March%205.%20However%2C%20state%20BJP%20president%20Manmohan%20Samal%20recently%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20form%20the%20government%20alone%20in%20the%20state%20and%20then%20later%20changed%20his%20stance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fodisha-bjp-presidents-flip-flop-on-alliance-with-bjd-sparks-uncertainty-ahead-of-polls%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia%20Bhatt's%20exciting%20upcoming%20films%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710491400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108516334%2Cimgsize-22790.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbrahmastra-2-love-and-war-jigra-alia-bhatts-exciting-upcoming-films%2Fphotostory%2F108516334.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108516334.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBrahmastra%202%2C%20Love%20and%20War%2C%20Jigra%3A%20Alia%20Bhatt's%20exciting%20upcoming%20films%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fb