words%20of%20his%20father%20and%20formative%20coach%20Naushad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20good%20that%20I%20got%20another%20year%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20IPL.%20I%20will%20understand%20T20%20cricket%20more%2C%20and%20how%20I%20should%20prepare%20for%20this%20format%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Musheer%2C%20who%20has%20so%20far%20played%20just%20five%20First-Class%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusheer%20embossed%20his%20name%20on%20the%20Ranji%20final%20against%20Vidarbha%20recently%20with%20a%20136%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20that%20helped%20Mumbai%20set%20a%20massive%20target%20of%20538.%20It%20eventually%20helped%20Mumbai%20land%20their%20record-extending%2042nd%20title%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderstandably%2C%20Musheer%20drew%20inspiration%20from%20his%20elder%20brother%20Sarfaraz%2C%20who%20made%20his%20India%20debut%20in%20the%20third%20Test%20against%20England%20at%20Rajkot%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20really%20inspired%20by%20my%20brother%20because%20of%20his%20dedication%20and%20the%20way%20he%20bats.%20Our%20batting%20style%20is%20similar.%20He%20told%20me%20before%20the%20game%20(Ranji%20final)%20to%20think%20of%20it%20as%20a%20normal%20match%20and%20not%20to%20take%20too%20much%20pressure.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BFrom%20outside%2C%20it%20may%20feel%20like%20a%20normal%20match%20but%20on%20the%20field%2C%20we%20feel%20pressure%20on%20the%20field.%20He%20told%20me%20to%20back%20my%20skills%20and%20follow%20the%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusheer%2C%20who%20was%20also%20the%20leading%20run-scorer%20in%20the%20ICC%20Under-19%20World%20Cup%20earlier%20this%20year%20including%20two%20hundreds%2C%20was%20quite%20chuffed%20after%20Mumbai's%20Ranji%20Trophy%20triumph%20after%20a%20gap%20of%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20matter%20of%20pride%20that%20we%20have%20amassed%2042%20titles.%20Many%20great%20players%20have%20played%20here%20(for%20Mumbai).%20I%20feel%20very%20proud%20that%20I%20have%20played%20for%20Mumbai%20and%20won%20a%20championship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20want%20to%20thank%20the%20Mumbai%20Cricket%20Association%20(MCA)%20and%20congratulate%20them%20because%20they%20have%20provided%20us%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20support.%20I%20hope%20they%20continue%20to%20back%20us%20in%20the%20same%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elegant%20right-hander%20lauded%20veteran%20pacer%20Dhawal%20Kulkarni%2C%20who%20retired%20after%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20support%20he%20has%20given%20to%20Mumbai%20cricket%2C%20the%20things%20he%20has%20done%20for%20Mumbai%2C%20it's%20incredible.%20The%20speech%20he%20gave%20ahead%20of%20the%20final%20was%20a%20real%20motivation%20for%20all%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20his%20last%20match.%20We%20were%20emotional%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20win%20the%20trophy%20as%20a%20gift%20to%20Dhawal%20bhai.%20We%20wanted%20him%20to%20leave%20happily.%20He%20took%20the%20last%20wicket%20(of%20Vidarbha)%20of%20the%20match%20and%20everything%20came%20out%20perfectly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710490140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fcun4vu_sarfaraz-naushad-musheer_625x300_13_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fmy-name-is-not-in-ipl-my-father-tells-me-sarfaraz-khans-brother-musheer-bares-his-heart-5242710%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Musheer%20Khan%20is%20happy%20that%20he%20went%20unsold%20during%20last%20year's%20player%20auction%20because%20it%20gives%20him%20some%20more%20time%20to%20%26quot%3Bunderstand%26quot%3B%20the%20T20%20format.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%