%20Varg-Pratham%20Varsh'%2C%2020-day%20'Sangh%20Shiksha%20Varg-Dvitya%20Varsh'%20and%2025-day%20'Sangh%20Shiksha%20Varg-Tritiya%20Varsh'%20training%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mr%20Vaidya%2C%20they%20now%20have%20a%203-day%20'Prarambhik%20Varg'%20programme%20for%20new%20Sangh%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20recruits%20will%20then%20take%20part%20in%20the%20'Prathamik%20Shiksha%20Varg'%20followed%20by%20a%2015-day%20'Sangh%20Shiksha%20Varg'%2C%20which%20was%20earlier%20called%20'Sangh%20Shiksha%20Varg-Pratham%20Varsh'%20and%20had%20a%20duration%20of%2020%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vaidya%20said%20that%20youth%20in%20large%20numbers%20are%20attending%20the%20Sangh%20training%20programmes.%20Every%20year%2C%2015%2C000%20to%2017%2C000%20young%20individuals%20participate%20in%20the%20'Pratham%20Shiksha%20Varg'%20(Pratham%20Varsh%20class)%20and%20about%201%20lakh%20in%20the%20'Prathamik%20Shiksha%20Varg'%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHenceforth%2C%20the%20'Sangh%20Shiksha%20Varg'%20(Pratham%20Varsh)%20will%20be%20for%2015%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Vaidya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20earlier%20training%20classes%20of%20'Dvitya%20Varsha'%20and%20'Tritya%20Varsh'%20will%20now%20be%20called%20'Karyakarta%20Vikas%20Varg-1'%20and%20'Karyakarta%20Vikas%20Varg-2'%2C%20respectively%2C%20said%20the%20RSS%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vaidya%20said%20that%20the%20content%20of%20'Tritya%20Varsh'%20class%20has%20been%20tweaked%20a%20bit%20to%20provide%20behavioural%20training%20to%20the%20trainees%20by%20taking%20them%20to%20the%20field%20for%205%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20new%20syllabus%20and%20nomenclature%20will%20be%20implemented%20from%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20there%20will%20be%20discussions%20on%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20during%20the%20RSS%20conclave%2C%20Mr%20Vaidya%20said%20Sangh%20always%20pitches%20for%20maximum%20voting%2C%2