rship-stunning-return-to-earth-moments-before-it-was-lost-5242748%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwatch-spacex-starship-stunning-return-to-earth-moments-before-it-was-lost-5242748%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Yodha%20-%20Insufferable%20Scrappy%20Thriller%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESaddled%20with%20a%20wayward%20screenplay%20that%20fires%20a%20string%20of%20blanks%2C%20%3Ci%3EYodha%3C%2Fi%3E%20fights%20a%20losing%20battle.%20The%20titular%20hero%20is%20a%20de-rostered%20soldier%20from%20a%20disbanded%20task%20force%20who%20boards%20a%20commercial%20aeroplane%20to%20nowhere.%20He%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20wreak%20vengeance%20and%20seek%20redemption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20what%20the%20screenplay%20by%20co-director%20Sagar%20Ambre%20lets%20on%20amid%20the%20pandemonium%20unleashed%20by%20wobbly%20planes%20and%20failing%20hydraulics.%20Everything%20in%20%3Ci%3EYodha%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20an%20insufferably%20scrappy%20thriller%2C%20is%20a%20bewildering%20blur.%20Figuring%20out%20what%20is%20going%20on%20is%20best%20left%20to%20troopers%20who%20have%20no%20fear%20of%20the%20unfathomable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20in%20the%20film%2C%20the%20protagonist%20walks%20out%20of%20a%20deep%20river%20with%20a%20smoke%20bomb%20in%20his%20hand.%20It%20emits%20the%20three%20colours%20of%20the%20national%20flag.%20The%20guy%20sure%20knows%20the%20technique%20to%20keep%20a%20smoke-flare%20dry%20in%20water.%20He%20does%20even%20better%20in%20the%20climax%20with%20another%20tricolour-spewing%20smoke%20bomb%20that%20survives%20an%20explosion%20and%20a%20full-blown%20inferno.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20how%20lenient%20you%20might%20want%20to%20be%20and%20how%20much%20of%20a%20Sidharth%20Malhotra%20fan%20you%20are%2C%20this%20pulpy%20action%20movie%20is%20a%20bumpy%20ride%20that%20lurches%20from%20one%20misstep%20to%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ci%3EYodha%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20passenger%20planes%20are%20mere%20playthings%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20commandos%20and%20terrorists.%20They%20can%20access%20the%20cargo%20hold%20from%20the%20cabin%20at%20will%2C%20which%2C%20as%20anybody%20who%20knows%20about%20planes%20will%20tell%20you%2C%20is%20simply%20not%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20action%20in%20%3Ci%3EYodha%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20directed%20by%20Ambre%20and%20Pushkar%20Ojha%2C%20unfolds%20in%20the%20passenger%20cabin%20of%20an%20aircraft%20and%20in%20the%20spaces%20under%20it.%20The%20film%20eventually%20winds%20up%20in%20an%20Islamabad%20building%20called%20Jinnah%20Hall%20where%20peace%20talks%20are%20underway%20between%20the%20premiers%20of%20India%20and%20Pakistan.%20No%20prizes%20for%20guessing%2C%20a%20terror%20plot%20is%20afoot%20alongside%20to%20scuttle%20the%20negotiations%20because%20war%2C%20the%20antagonist%20thunders%2C%20is%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPassengers%20on%20the%20aircraft%20commandeered%20by%20the%20protagonist%20are%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20a%20yarn%20that%20hits%20severe%20turbulence%20and%20goes%20into%20an%20unending%20tailspin.%20They%20can%20only%20gawk%20and%20shriek%20in%20horror%20at%20the%20harebrained%2C%20ham-fisted%20lows%20that%20Yodha%20and%20his%20flying%20machine%20descends%20to.%20The%20film%20revels%20in%20blowing%20logic%20and%20common%20sense%20to%20smithereens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EYodha%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20showcase%20for%20the%20exploits%20of%20a%20highly%20trained%20soldier%20who%20is%20wronged%20by%20the%20system.%20He%20is%20made%20the%20scapegoat%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20VIP%20-%20a%20nuclear%20scientist%2C%20no%20less%20-%20on%20a%20hijacked%20flight.%20His%20unit%2C%20the%20elite%20Yodha%20Task%20Force%20made%20up%20of%20the%20best%20soldiers%20from%20the%20Army%2C%20Navy%20and%20Air%20Force%2C%20is%20unceremoniously%20axed%20and%20the%20men%20transferred%20without%20a%20by-your-leave%20to%20other%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArun%20Katyal%20(Sidharth%20Malhotra)%2C%20son%20of%20a%20martyr%2C%20refuses%20to%20admit%20that%20he%20was%20at%20fault.%20He%20bides%20his%20time%20to%20strike%20back%20and%20reclaim%20his%20lost%20glory.%20When%20his%20time%20does%20come%2C%20he%20ends%20up%20on%20a%20Delhi%20to%20London%20flight%20in%20a%20mysterious%20manner%20that%20leaves%20everybody%20on%20board%20guessing.%20If%20the%20idea%20is%20to%20flummox%20those%20watching%20the%20spectacle%2C%20%3Ci%3EYodha%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20a%20success.%20There%20is%20nary%20a%20scene%20in%20the%20film%20that%20makes%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20brief%20prelude%2C%20the%20body%20of%20a%20fallen%20soldier%2C%20Surender%20Katyal%20(Ronit%20Roy%20in%20a%20cameo)%2C%20is%20brought%20home%20in%20a%20wooden%20casket.%20Cut%20to%20the%20Indo-Bangladeshi%20border%2C%20where%20Arun%20Katyal%20goes%20after%20a%20band%20of%20evil%20men%20(they%20could%20be%20smugglers%20or%20infiltrators%20or%20terrorists%2C%20there%20is%20no%20way%20of%20knowing)%20and%20summarily%20eliminates%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20early%20sequence%20is%20obviously%20meant%20to%20establish%20how%20Arun%20Katyal%20operates%20-%20he%20does%20not%20believe%20in%20negotiations%20or%20in%20issuing%20warnings%20before%20pulling%20the%20trigger.%20Yes%2C%20he%20takes%20no%20prisoners%20nor%20does%20he%20wait%20for%20orders.%20The%20streak%20of%20impatience%20lands%20him%20in%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sloppy%20screenplay%20fails%20to%20create%20any%20sort%20of%20convincing%20context%20for%20the%20methods%20that%20the%20hero%20employs%2C%20let%20alone%20tell%20the%20audience%20why%20the%20young%20man%20is%20forever%20spoiling%20for%20a%20skirmish%20where%20a%20little%20coaxing%20could%20be%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEverything%20is%20purely%20personal%20for%20the%20patriot.%20He%20is%20a%20soldier%20because%20his%20father%20laid%20down%20his%20life%20for%20the%20nation.%20The%20senior%20bureaucrat%20who%20deposes%20against%20him%20after%20a%20botched%20mission%20is%20Priyamvada%20Katyal%20(Raashii%20Khanna)%2C%20his%20wife.%20He%20is%20punished%20for%20breaking%20the%20chain%20of%20command.%20Worse%2C%20Priyamvada%2C%20putting%20nation%20before%20self%2C%20files%20for%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20family%20friend%20and%20Arun's%20colleague%20(Tanuj%20Virwani)%20-%20he%20is%20simply%20Khan%2C%20the%20token%20good%20Muslim%20that%20no%20such%20patriotism-peddling%20thriller%20can%20do%20without%20-%20tries%20in%20vain%20to%20talk%20the%20couple%20out%20of%20their%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArun%20Katyal's%20life%20and%20career%20are%20in%20a%20shambles%20because%20he%20-%20again%20this%20is%20what%20one%20can%20only%20surmise%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20driblets%20of%20information%20that%20the%20script%20throws%20at%20us%20-%20has%20a%20score%20to%20settle%20with%20a%20terrorist%20who%20pushed%20him%20off%20a%20plane%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20into%20a%20black%20hole%20that%20continues%20to%20haunt%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F3AuB8RTfBJc%3Fsi%3D2YSPGjiL9hWtx3lX%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20hijack%20situation%2C%20the%20head%20purser%20of%20the%20plane%20(Disha%20Patani)%20struts%20around%20like%20a%20catwalk%20model%20until%20she%20is%20ready%20to%20reveal%20her%20true%20colours%20and%20jump%20into%20the%20thick%20of%20the%20action.%20The%20first%20officer%20in%20the%20cockpit%2C%20too%2C%20has%20plans%20that%20catch%20the%20hero%20by%20surprise.%20There%20are%20several%20all-out%20fights%20in%20the%20aisle%2C%20the%20toilet%20and%20the%20cargo%20hold%20even%20as%20the%20plane%20loses%20height%20and%20strays%20off%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20on%20board%20is%20an%20intern%20-%20she%20claims%20she%20has%20200%20hours%20of%20flying%20experience%20-%20who%20is%20forced%20to%20take%20control%20of%20the%20aircraft%20when%20the%20crisis%20escalates.%20Do%20not%20try%20to%20put%20two%20and%20two%20together%20because%20nothing%20that%20%3Ci%3EYodha%3C%2Fi%3E%20stacks%20up%20actually%20adds%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20too%20much%20to%20expect%20Sidharth%20Malhotra%20to%20pull%20this%20mess%20out%20of%20the%20dumps.%20He%20leaps%20around%2C%20runs%2C%20throws%20punches%2C%20fires%20in%20all%20directions%20and%20holds%20his%20ground%20as%20bedlam%20erupts%20around%20him%20-%20most%20of%20it%20of%20his%20own%20making%20-%20but%20the%20actor%20cannot%20rise%20above%20the%20muddle%20that%20%3Ci%3EYodha%3C%2Fi%3E%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20other%20actors%20in%20the%20cast%2C%20they%20go%20through%20the%20motions.%20Their%20faces%20give%20nothing%20away.%20Is%20this%20the%20stoicism%20of%20the%20brave%3F%20No%2C%20it%20is%20a%20sign%20that%20they%2C%20like%20the%20audience%2C%20are%20clueless.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710486180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fsq17j53o_yodha_625x300_15_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fyodha-review-insufferable-scrappy-thriller-1-5-stars-5242742%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yodha%20Review%3A%20No%20matter%20how%20lenient%20you%20might%20want%20to%20be%20and%20how%20much%20of%20a%20Sidharth%20Malhotra%20fan%20you%20are%2C%20this%20pulpy%20action%20movie%20is%20a%20bumpy%20ride%20that%20lurches%20from%20one%20misstep%20to%20another.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fyodha-review-insufferable-scrappy-thriller-1-5-stars-5242742%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Irish%20Wish%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Lindsay%20Lohan%20Stars%20in%20a%20Synthetic%20Magical%20Rom-Com%20Trifle%2C%20but%20Her%20Chemistry%20With%20Ed%20Speleers%20Is%20No%20Blarney%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A17104860