during%20the%20early%20months%20of%20the%20year%20when%20farmers%20often%20burn%20crops%20to%20clear%20land%2C%20and%20forest%20fires%20and%20exhaust%20fumes%20also%20add%20to%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERising%20awareness%20of%20the%20health%20implications%20has%20prompted%20some%20action%20from%20the%20government%2C%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Srettha%20Thavisin's%20cabinet%20approving%20a%20Clean%20Air%20Act%20to%20tackle%20the%20issue%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20premier%20is%20also%20due%20to%20visit%20later%20Friday%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20meet%20with%20organisations%20tackling%20forest%20fires%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Chiang%20Mai%20residents%20--%20like%20orange%20seller%20Kamol%2C%20who%20sighed%20and%20shook%20his%20head%20when%20asked%20--%20said%20they%20had%20received%20no%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20need%20to%20get%20my%20health%20checked%20every%20year%2C%20especially%20for%20respiratory%20diseases%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20government%20agency%20warned%20this%20month%20that%20more%20official%20action%20was%20needed%2C%20saying%20at%20least%2010%20million%20people%20required%20treatment%20for%20pollution-related%20health%20problems%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pollution%20is%20always%20high%2C%20especially%20this%20time%20of%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20said%2050-year-old%20Sariya%20while%20shopping%20for%20groceries%20in%20Chiang%20Mai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20nothing%20we%20can%20do%20about%20it%20since%20it's%20always%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESariya%2C%20who%20gave%20only%20one%20name%2C%20also%20said%20the%20city's%20location%20--%20nestled%20between%20hills%2C%20trapping%20the%20toxic%20smog%20--%20made%20the%20situation%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bmore%20worried%26quot%3B%20about%20people%20living%20there%20with%20underlying%20health%20issues%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20help%