ayments%2520Bank%2520will%2520stop%2Cthe%2520Reserve%2520Bank%2520of%2520India.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erule%20violations%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Customers%20relying%20on%20digital%20payments%20are%20advised%20to%20find%20alternative%20banking%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThese%20services%20to%20stop%20from%20today%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPaytm%20Payments%20Bank%20customers%20can%20no%20longer%20deposit%20money%20into%20their%20accounts%2C%20but%20can%20still%20withdraw%20or%20transfer%20funds.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUsers%20will%20no%20longer%20get%20salary%20credits%2C%20direct%20benefit%20transfers%2C%20and%20subsidies%20in%20their%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20account%2C%20but%20will%20still%20continue%20to%20get%20refunds%2C%20cashbacks%2C%20and%20sweep-ins%20from%20partner%20banks.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUsers%20cannot%20top-up%20their%20wallets%20or%20transfer%20funds%20from%20their%20Paytm%20wallet%2C%20however%2C%20they%20can%20still%20use%20the%20money%20in%20their%20wallet%20to%20pay%20bills.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECustomers%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20recharge%20their%20FASTag%20issued%20by%20the%20Paytm%20bank.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERecharging%20NCMC%20cards%20from%20Paytm%20Bank%20will%20not%20be%20possible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUsers%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20transfer%20funds%20into%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20accounts%20through%20UPI%20or%20IMPS.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECustomers%20can%20still%20use%20their%20Paytm%20balance%20to%20pay%20for%20subscriptions%2C%20but%20they%20will%20have%20to%20use%20a%20different%20bank%20account%20from%20March%2015.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Paytm%20app%20will%20keep%20running%20even%20after%20March%2015.%20Your%20services%20will%20not%20be%20affected%20if%20you%20do%20not%20have%20a%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20account.%20You%20can%20still%20use%20UPI%20services%20through%20the%20Paytm%20app%2C%20as%20long%20as%20it%20is%20linked%20to%