0account%26quot%3B%20of%20her%20death.%20The%20lawsuit%20also%20accuses%20Fox%20of%20promoting%20the%20book%20%26quot%3Bfor%20the%20purpose%20of%20deceiving%20Sasha's%20parents%20and%20the%20public%20about%20Fox's%20wrongful%20conduct%20and%20accountability%20for%20Sasha's%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20actual%20circumstances%20of%20Sasha's%20death%20%E2%80%94%20which%20contradict%20the%20official%20accounts%20given%20by%20Fox%2C%20Ben%20Hall%2C%20and%20Harper%20Collins%20%E2%80%94%20were%20only%20uncovered%20through%20investigation%20by%20their%20counsel%20almost%20two%20years%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges.%20%26quot%3BNew%20information%20and%20new%20contradictions%2C%20are%20still%20being%20uncovered%20to%20this%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarperCollins%20is%20included%20as%20a%20defendant%20in%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20is%20also%20included%20as%20a%20defendant%2C%20but%20Kuvshynova's%20attorneys%20acknowledged%20in%20the%20lawsuit%20that%20he%20may%20be%20more%20%26quot%3Bproperly%20aligned%20in%20this%20litigation%20as%20a%20party-plaintiff%20victim%20of%20Fox%20Defendants'%20wrongful%20conduct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarperCollins%20and%20Hall%2C%20each%20contacted%20outside%20working%20hours%2C%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Fox%20News%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20detailed%20questions%20but%20released%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20understand%20the%20grief%20and%20continue%20to%20mourn%20the%20loss%20of%20both%20Pierre%20Zakrzewski%20and%20Sasha%20Kuvshynova%2C%20we%20will%20respectfully%20defend%20against%20the%20inaccurate%20claims%20within%20this%20lawsuit%2C%26quot%3B%20Fox%20News%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%20%26quot%3BThe%20safety%20of%20our%20journalists%20has%20always%20been%20our%20number%20one%20priority%2C%20and%20we%20are%20immensely%20grateful%20to%20the%20Fox%20News%20journalists%20who%20have%20covered%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20we%20remain%20committed%20to%20reporting%20from%20the%20region.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20warnings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20%26quot%3Boverworked%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bunderstaffed%26quot%3B%20crew%20for%20Fox%20News%20remained%20in%20Kyiv%20as%20Russian%20forces%20began%20pushing%20toward%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20capital%20in%20March%202022%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKuvshynova%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewas%20hired%20in%20January%20as%20an%20independent%20contractor%20to%20act%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bguide%20and%20translator%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20Fox%20News%20team%2C%20court%20documents%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20alleges%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20of%20Kuvshynova%20being%20paid%20for%20the%20two%20months%20she%20was%20with%20Fox%20News%20and%20no%20evidence%20that%20she%20was%20hired%20in%20accordance%20with%20local%20Ukrainian%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fox%20News%20crew%20received%20multiple%20warnings%20to%20avoid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-says-retaken-irpin-city-outside-kyiv-from-russia-forces-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIrpin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20town%20northwest%20of%20Kyiv%2C%20and%20the%20adjacent%20suburb%20of%20Hostomel%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges.%20Both%20areas%20were%20being%20occupied%20by%20Russian%20forces%2C%20and%20where%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20were%20launching%20a%20counterattack%20by%20March%2013%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20how%20close%20Russian%20forces%20were%20to%20the%20two%20towns%20and%20the%20towns'%20proximity%20to%20Kyiv%2C%20where%20Fox%20News'%20teams%20were%20based%2C%20%26quot%3BFox%20left%20the%20news%20crew%20in%20place%26quot%3B%20without%20the%20%26quot%3Bevaluation%2C%20monitoring%2C%20and%20vetting%20of%20story%20assignments%26quot%3B%20normally%20performed%20by%20producers%2