s%20made%20their%20way%20back%20on%20the%20main%20road%20to%20Kyiv%20in%20their%20vehicle%2C%20the%20crew%20stopped%2C%20and%20then%20%26quot%3Btwo%20explosive%20rounds%20hit%20near%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20some%20of%20the%20crew%20scurried%20out%20of%20the%20car%20to%20escape%20the%20clear%20and%20present%20danger%2C%20a%20third%20round%20hit%20the%20car%2C%20with%20Sasha%20inside%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges.%20%26quot%3BThe%20car%20caught%20fire%2C%20and%20Sasha%20was%20burned%20to%20ashes%20inside%20it%2C%20causing%20her%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZakrzewski%20escaped%20the%20car%20but%20bled%20to%20death%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20road%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%20Hall%20was%20found%20%26quot%3Bgrievously%20injured%20at%20the%20side%20of%20the%20road%26quot%3B%20and%20later%20evacuated%20by%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%2C%20per%20the%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20aftermath%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFox%20News%20said%20it%20knew%20the%20crew's%20location%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20contests%20that%20claim%2C%20saying%20a%20search%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bmissing%20crew%26quot%3B%20was%20launched%20on%20March%2014%20after%20Halls'%20team%20did%20not%20return%20to%20Kyiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20security%20team%20knew%20exactly%20where%20they%20were.%20We%20knew%20where%20we%20dropped%20them%20off%2C%20where%20they%20were%20going%2C%20and%20where%20they%20ended%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Fox%20News%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20lawyers%20for%20Kuvshynova's%20parents%20accused%20Fox%20News%20of%20failing%20to%20explain%20why%20the%20crew%20pursued%20an%20assignment%20that%20was%20prohibited%20by%20Ukrainian%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suit%20accuses%20Fox%20News%20of%20violating%20%26quot%3Bany%20reasonable%20standard%20of%20care%20in%20allowing%20the%20team%20to%20proceed%26quot%3B%20into%20the%20active%20war%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20day%2C%20Fox%20News%20continues%20to%20withhold%20information%20about%20Kuvshynova's%20death%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMia%20Jankowicz%20contributed%20to%20this%20report.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-journalist-oleksandra-sasha-kuvshynova-sues-fox-news-wrongful-death-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710483178000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f37c023037f8e81750a433%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-journalist-oleksandra-sasha-kuvshynova-sues-fox-news-wrongful-death-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20team%20of%20Fox%20News%20employees%2C%20including%20Oleksandra%20%26quot%3BSasha%26quot%3B%20Kuvshynova%2C%20pushed%20into%20a%20war%20zone%20despite%20warnings%20to%20stay%20out%2C%20lawsuit%20alleges.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-journalist-oleksandra-sasha-kuvshynova-sues-fox-news-wrongful-death-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Unique%20Numbers%20Recorded%20by%20SBI'%3A%20Investigative%20Journalist%20Who%20Bought%20Electoral%20Bond%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F15114049%2FPoonam-Agarwal.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Even%20as%20we%20try%20to%20get%20a%20finer%20understanding%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20data%20released%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20on%20Thursday%2C%20several%20observers%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-issues-notice-to-sbi-for-not-releasing-unique-numbers-linked-to-electoral-bonds-bought-redeemed%5C%22%3Eand%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20divulged%20the%20unique%20identification%20number%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds.%20The%20number%2C%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmatching%20code%E2%80%9D%2C%20could%20have%20established%20a%20connection%20between%20the%20purchaser%20of%20the%20bond%20and%20the%20beneficiary%20political%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20now%20issued%20notice%20to%20the%20SBI%20on%20its%20failure%20to%20disclose%20these%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Edid%20a%20quick%20chat%20with%20Poonam%20Agarwal%2C%20who%2C%20back%20in%202018%20as%20a%20journalist%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Quint%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20of%20the%20first%20Indian%20scribes%20to%20buy%20an%20electoral%20bond%20for%20an%20investigative%20story.%20Read%20her%20experience%20and%20explanation%20on%20why%20she%20feels%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmatching%20code%E2%80%9D%2C%20if%20divulged%2C%20would%20have%20painted%20a%20much%20more%20vivid%20picture%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20story%20than%20it%20is%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAs%20one%20of%20the%20first%20journalists%20to%20buy%20an%20electoral%20bond%2C%20could%20you%20give%20us%20an%20idea%20of%20the%20process%20of%20purchasing%20the%20EBs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20the%20SBI%20Parliament%20Branch%20to%20purchase%20the%20bond%2C%20the%20only%20branch%20in%20Delhi%20that%20sells%20electoral%20bonds.%20I%20went%20as%20a%20citizen%20of%20the%20country%20to%20purchase%20the%20bond.%20The%20SBI%20officer%20checked%20why%20I%20am%20interested%20in%20purchasing%20the%20bond%2C%20I%20told%20him%20that%20I%20am%20interested%20in%20donating%20to%20political%20parties%20through%20the%20bond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDid%20you%20find%20the%20whole%20purchasing%20process%20hush-hush%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20officers%20were%20a%20bit%20suspicious%20about%20me%20as%20to%20why%20an%20individual%20had%20come%20to%20purchase%20the%20bond.%20And%20from%20where%20did%20I%20get%20to%20know%20about%20bonds.%20They%20took%20my%20KYC%20details%20and%20a%20cheque%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20before%20selling%20the%20bond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20had%20mentioned%20in%20your%20story%20that%20each%20EB%20had%20a%20unique%20identification%20number.%20How%20did%20you%20find%20it%3F%20And%20what%20could%20have%20been%20its%20use%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20my%20curiosity%20that%20made%20me%20get%20a%20forensic%20test%20done%20of%20the%20bond.%20When%20I%20gave%20my%20Rs%201%2C000%20bond%20to%20the%20Truth%20lab%20forensic%20lab%20to%20test%2C%20they%20said%20that%20there%20is%20a%20hidden%20unique%20number%20which%20is%20visible%20under%20UV%20Ray.%20To%20prove%20that%20it%20is%20a%20unique%20number%2C%20I%20purchased%20one%20more%20bond%20worth%20Rs%201%2C000%20and%20got%20its%20forensic%20test%20done.%20Both%20the%20bonds%20had%20different%20numbers%20hidden%20in%20the%20bonds.%20Hence%20it%20was%20proven%20that%20bonds%20carry%20hidden%20unique%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESBI%20in%20an%20RTI%20reply%20confirmed%20that%20these%20unique%20numbers%20were%20recorded%20and%20it%20is%20used%20for%20audit%20trail.%20The%20finance%20ministry%20responded%20to%20my%20story%20saying%20that%20the%20unique%20hidden%20number%20is%20a%20security%20feature.%20So%20both%20are%20true%2C%20it%20is%20a%20security%20feature%20and%20also%20used%20for%20audit%20trail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20SBI%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20to%20the%20SC%20seeking%20over%20three%20months%20to%20submit%20the%20details%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20was%20quashed.%20And%20within%20a%20day%2C%20the%20SBI%20could%20furnish%20those%20details%20to%20the%20ECI%2C%20which%20has%20now%20published%20it.%20What%20do%20you%20think%20could%20be%20the%20SBI%E2%80%99s%20reasons%20to%20seek%20more%20time%2C%20if%20the%20data%20was%20already%20readily%20available%20with%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20journalist%2C%20I%20cannot%20say%20why%20SBI%20is%20not%20taking%20a%20plea%20of%20time%20for%20not%20matching%20the%20data%20of%20the%20purchaser%20and%20political%20parties.%20I%20can%20only%20state%20facts%2C%20and%20the%20facts%20are%20that%20these%20unique%20numbers%20are%20recorded%20and%20SBI%20conducts%20an%20audit%20trail%20every%20financial%20year.%20Then%20how%20come%20they%20have%20not%20compiled%20and%20matched%20the%20data%20of%20the%20purchaser%20and%20the%20political%20parties%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710483103000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F15114049%2FPoonam-Agarwal.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Funique-numbers-recorded-by-sbi-investigative-journalist-who-bought-electoral-bond%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSBI%20in%20an%20RTI%20reply%20confirmed%20that%20these%20unique%20numbers%20were%20recorded%20and%20it%20is%20used%20for%20audit%20trail.%20The%20finance%20ministry%20responded%20to%20my%20story%20saying%20that%20the%20unique%20hidden%20number%20is%20a%20security%20feature.%20So%20both%20are%20true%2C%20it%20is%20a%20security%20feature%20and%20also%20used%20for%20audit%20trail.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Funique-numbers-recorded-by-sbi-investigative-journalist-who-bought-electoral-bond%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Soil%20Being%20Used%20For%20Terror%20Against%20India%2C%20Indian-Americans%20Inform%20FBI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20eminent%20Indian-Americans%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20has%20held%20a%20special%20meeting%20with%20senior%20officials%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%2C%20FBI%20and%20police%20and%20told%20that%20the%20US%20soil%20is%20being%20used%20for%20terrorist%20activities%20against%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20held%20the%20meeting%20with%20senior%20officials%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%2C%20FBI%20and%20local%20police%20this%20week%20on%20increasing%20hate%20crimes%20against%20Hindus%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20meeting%2C%20Indian-Americans%20expressed%20their%20displeasure%20and%20dissatisfaction%20that%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20in%20the%20US%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20take%20any%20action%20against%20those%20who%20are%20espousing%20terrorism%20activities%20in%20India%2C%20according%20to%20multiple%20persons%20present%20in%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20to%20address%20the%20challenging%20issue%20of%20the%20rise%20in%20hate%20crimes%20against%20Hindu%20and%20Jain%20places%20of%20worship%20was%20held%20at%20the%20initiative%20of%20community%20leader%20Ajai%20Jain%20Bhutoria.%20It%20was%20attended%20by%20about%20two%20dozen%20eminent%20Indian-Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVincent%20Plair%20and%20Harpreet%20Singh%20Mokha%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice's%20Community%20Relations%20Service%20along%20with%20FBI%20officials%20and%20those%20from%20the%20police%20departments%20of%20San%20Francisco%2C%20Milpitas%2C%20Freemont%20and%20Newark%20attended%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sudden%20increase%20in%20hate%20crimes%20against%20Indian-Americans%20in%20general%20and%20the%20Hindus%20in%20particular%20is%20causing%20a%20lot%20of%20fear%20and%20anxiety%20in%20the%20community%2C%20said%20the%20Indian-Americans%20after%20the%20meeting%20which%20was%20closed%20to%20the%20press.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20fear%20in%20the%20community%20right%20now.%20The%20Khalistan%20people%20park%20trucks%20outside%20schools%2C%20and%20Indian%20grocery%20stores%20and%20intimidate%20young%20Indian-Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20community%20members%20expressed%20their%20anger%20that%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20take%20any%20action%20against%20those%20people%2C%20including%20those%20who%20tried%20to%20burn%20the%20Indian%20consulate%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20and%20are%20openly%20threatening%20Indian%20diplomats%20and%20giving%20open%20calls%20for%20terrorist%20incidents%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20members%20present%20in%20the%20meeting%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20that%20senior%20law%20enforcement%20officials%20said%20that%20they%20were%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20Khalistan%20movement%20in%20the%20US%20and%20wanted%20the%20Indian%20Americans%20to%20help%20them%20raise%20awareness%20about%20these%20terrorist%20groups%20in%20the%20US.%20They%20also%20said%20that%20they%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20take%20action%20because%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20resources%20and%20funds%20and%20that%20they%20have%20other%20top%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20meeting%20was%20a%20crucial%20moment%20as%20we%20united%20to%20confront%20the%20recent%20surge%20in%20hate%20crimes%20targeting%20Hindu%20places%20of%20worship.%20I%20brought%20together%20Indian%20community%20leaders%2C%20DOJ%2C%20FBI%2C%20and%20law%20enforcement%20officials%20from%20Milpitas%2C%20SF%2C%20Fremont%2C%20and%20Newark.%20In%20the%20last%20four%20months%2C%20over%2011%20temples%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20alone%20have%20been%20attacked%2C%20vandalised%2C%20and%20defaced%20with%20hateful%20graffiti.%20The%20fear%20in%20our%20community%20is%20palpable%2C%20but%20our%20collective%20resolve%20is%20stronger%20than%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhutoria%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20delved%20into%20safeguarding%20places%20of%20worship%20and%20tackling%20hate%20crimes%2C%20notably%20those%20involving%20Sikhs%20for%20Justice%20(SFJ)%20Khalistani%20supporters%20targeting%20Hindu%20Temples%2C%20displaying%20disturbing%20banners%20in%20front%20of%20schools%20and%20corporate%20establishments.%20In%20our%20discourse%2C%20we%20explored%20the%20prospect%20of%20organising%20a%20Protecting%20all%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Forum%20(PPOW)%20with%20the%20DOJ%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sikh%20leader%20Sukhi%20Chahal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chahal%20said%20he%20personally%20underscored%20the%20significance%20of%20addressing%20the%20provocative%20and%20threatening%20video%20messages%20from%20SFJ%20pro-Khalistan%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20urged%20FBI%20and%20DOJ%20officials%20to%20earnestly%20consider%20the%20potential%20repercussions%20of%20Mr%20Pannu's%20statements%20on%20peace%2C%20harmony%2C%20and%20India-US%20relations.%20It%20is%20paramount%20that%20we%20collectively%20work%20to%20mitigate%20the%20impact%20of%20such%20hateful%20messages%2C%20which%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20disturb%20societal%20tranquillity%20and%20radicalise%20the%20youth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20meeting%2C%20it%20was%20agreed%20that%20a%20working%20group%20will%20be%20formed%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20that%20will%20actively%20pursue%20safety%20measures%20at%20places%20of%20worship%20and%20systemic%20reporting%20of%20any%20unwanted%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20working%20group%20would%20have%20representations%20from%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20leaders%20expressed%20concerns%20that%20the%20police%20were%20not%20of%20much%20help%20to%20them%20in%20either%20addressing%20this%20increasing%20fear%20or%20stopping%20terror%20activities%20from%20the%20US%20against%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20pressed%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20Khalistan%2C%20the%20law%20enforcement%20officials%20said%20that%20they%20don't%20understand%20the%20context%20and%20they%20need%20to%20be%20educated%20on%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20Indian%20Americans%20told%20the%20FBI%20that%20the%20Khalist