%20India%20for%20not%20releasing%20the%20bond%20numbers%20in%20the%20electoral%20bond%20data%20submitted%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20which%20the%20EC%20made%20public%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felection-commission-uploads-electoral-bonds-data%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20data%20uploaded%20to%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20website%20makes%20it%20rather%20difficult%20to%20infer%20whether%20there%20were%20any%20quid%20pro%20quo%20dealings%20between%20companies%20which%20bought%20the%20bonds%20and%20different%20governments.%20The%20commission%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eci.gov.in%2Fdisclosure-of-electoral-bonds%5C%22%3Euploaded%20two%20sets%20of%20data%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20file%20contains%20a%20date-wise%20list%20of%20bond%20purchases%20by%20companies%20and%20the%20other%20file%20contains%20a%20date-wise%20list%20of%20deposits%20by%20political%20parties%20that%20encashed%20the%20bonds.%20Without%20the%20bond%20numbers%20being%20made%20available%20in%20either%20list%2C%20it%20was%20not%20possible%20to%20cross-verify%20which%20company%20or%20individual%20was%20donating%20to%20which%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20asked%20for%20the%20SBI%E2%80%99s%20representative%2C%20who%20was%20not%20present%2C%20to%20answer%20for%20this%20unavailability%20of%20data.%20The%20court%20was%20hearing%20an%20application%20from%20the%20Election%20Commission%20on%20return%20of%20documents%20which%20ha%20been%20shared%20with%20the%20court%20in%20a%20sealed%20envelope.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20ask%20the%20office%20to%20scan%20and%20digitise%20the%20data%2C%20it%20may%20take%20a%20day%E2%80%A6as%20soon%20as%20the%20data%20is%20scanned%2C%20the%20originals%20will%20be%20returned%20to%20the%20ECI%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20said%20on%20this%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20the%20CJI%20himself%20brought%20up%20the%20matter%20pertaining%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20complete%20data%20released%20by%20the%20SBI.%20%E2%80%9CWho%20is%20appearing%20for%20the%20SBI%3F%20They%20have%20not%20disclosed%20the%20bond%20numbers.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20disclosed%20by%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20details%20have%20to%20be%20published%20by%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%20read%20out%20the%20operative%20part%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20earlier%20judgment%2C%20which%20said%20that%20all%20relevant%20details%20had%20to%20be%20published%20by%20the%20SBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20said%20in%20its%20judgment%20striking%20down%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20that%20voters%20have%20the%20right%20to%20know%20whether%20there%20have%20been%20any%20quid%20pro%20quo%20arrangements%20between%20parties%20in%20government%20and%20business%20houses%20or%20corporate%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Ftop-electoral-bond-purchasers-include-some-companies-that-were-raided-or-under-the-scanner%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20several%20of%20the%20companies%20listed%20as%20big%20purchasers%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20have%20been%20under%20the%20scanner%20of%20central%20agencies%20and%20faced%20cases%20and%20raids.%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reporters-collective.in%2Ftrc%2Fcompany-with-reliance-links-third-largest-donor%5C%22%3EOther%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0have%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20some%20companies%20have%20bought%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20much%20more%20than%20their%20annual%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710480656000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F0210263