%20times%20to%20save%20119%20people%20in%20the%20strait%20over%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20Taiwan's%20coast%20guard%20chief%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-taiwan-still-joining-forces-sea-rescues-war-fears-brew-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Agency%20Probes%20Risks%20Of%20Foreign%20Satellite%20Use%20By%20Handheld%20Devices%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Communications%20Commission%20said%20Thursday%20it%20is%20investigating%20if%20the%20use%20of%20Russian%20and%20Chinese%20foreign%20satellite%20systems%20by%20U.S.%20mobile%20phones%20and%20other%20devices%20poses%20security%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FCC%20has%20concerns%20U.S.%20handheld%20devices%20are%20receiving%20and%20processing%20Global%20Navigation%20Satellite%20System%20(GNSS)%20signals%20from%20satellites%20controlled%20by%20foreign%20adversaries%20in%20violation%20of%20commission%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FCC%20is%20seeking%20answers%20from%20handset%20manufacturers%20Apple%2C%20Google%2C%20Motorola%2C%20Nokia%2C%20Samsung%20and%20others%20that%20collectively%20cover%20over%2090%25%20of%20the%20U.S.%20smartphone%20marketplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20established%20record%20of%20what%20security%20threats%2C%20if%20any%2C%20these%20signals%20carry%20and%20whether%20the%20manufacturers%20of%20handheld%20devices%20are%20processing%20these%20signals%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20Commission's%20rules%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20FCC%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresentative%20Mike%20Gallagher%2C%20chair%20of%20the%20House%20Select%20China%20Committee%2C%20wrote%20FCC%20Chair%20Jessica%20Rosenworcel%20earlier%20this%20week%20raising%20concern%20about%20reports%20that%20U.S.%20cell%20phones%20were%20receiving%20and%20processing%20signals%20from%20Chinese%20and%20Russian%20satellites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FCC%20has%20only%20approved%20U.S.%20phones%20to%20receivers%20to%20receive%20and%20process%20signals%20from%20the%20U.S.%20Global%20Positioning%20System%20(GPS)%20and%20only%20the%20European%20Galileo%20GNSS%20has%20been%20approved.%20Gallagher%20said%20U.S.%20devices%20are%20receiving%20signals%20from%20the%20PRC%20BeiDou%20and%20Russian%20GLONASS%20GNSS%20constellations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCurrent%20events%20in%20Eastern%20Europe%20(including%20significant%20Russian%20jamming%20and%20spoofing%20of%20GNSS%20signals)%20call%20into%20question%20the%20wisdom%20of%20accepting%20this%20workaround%20and%20suggest%20it%20is%20critical%20that%20the%20FCC%20enforce%20its%20rules%20against%20using%20unauthorized%20signals%20from%20foreign%20satellites%2C%26quot%3B%20Gallagher%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERosenworcel%20in%202018%20raised%20concerns%20saying%20U.S.%20phones%20have%20chips%20designed%20to%20operate%20with%20global%20navigation%20satellite%20systems%20of%20other%20countries.%20%26quot%3BMany%20devices%20in%20the%20United%20States%20are%20already%20operating%20with%20foreign%20signals%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FCC%20wants%20to%20know%20%26quot%3Bwhether%20their%20devices%20are%20in%20compliance%20with%20FCC%20rules%20and%20what%20vulnerabilities%26quot%3B%20may%20exist%20in%20how%20they%20process%20GNSS%20signals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710479760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fm0cidano_federal-communications-commission-reuters_625x300_15_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-agency-probes-risks-of-foreign-satellite-use-by-handheld-devices-5242240%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Federal%20Communications%20Commission%20said%20Thursday%20it%20is%20investigating%20if%20the%20use%20of%20Russian%20and%20Chinese%20foreign%20satellite%20systems%20by%20US%20mobile%20phones%20and%20other%20devices%20poses%20security%20threats.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-agency-probes-risks-of-foreign-satellite-use-by-handheld-devices-5242240%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-agency-probes-risks-of-foreign-satellite-use-by-handheld-devices-5242240%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-agency-probes-risks-of-foreign-satellite-use-by-handheld-devices-5242240%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Electoral%20Bonds%20Data%20Exposes%20BJP's%20%26quot%3BCorrupt%20Tactics%26quot%3B%3A%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20on%20Friday%20alleged%20that%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20data%20has%20exposed%20%26quot%3Bcorrupt%20tactics%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20BJP%20such%20as%20quid%20pro%20quo%2C%20seeking%20donations%20for%20the%20company's%20protection%2C%20kickbacks%20and%20money%20laundering%20through%20shell%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20general%20secretary%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20also%20said%20the%20party%20continues%20to%20demand%20unique%20bond%20ID%20numbers%2C%20so%20that%20it%20can%20precisely%20match%20donors%20to%20recipients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Mr%20Ramesh%20put%20out%20a%20%26quot%3Bquick%20first%20analysis%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Electoral%20Bonds%20(EB)data%20disclosure%20that%20the%20SBI%20put%20out%20after%20weeks%20of%20%26quot%3Battempting%20to%20postpone%20it%20until%20after%20the%20election%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%201%2C300%20companies%20and%20individuals%20have%20donated%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20including%20over%206%2C000%20crore%20to%20the%20BJP%20since%202019%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F17165220%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20data%20exposes%20at%20least%20four%20corrupt%20tactics%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20Mr%20Ramesh%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQuid%20Pro%20Quo%3A%20There%20are%20many%20cases%20of%20companies%20that%20have%20donated%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20and%20immediately%20afterwards%20gotten%20huge%20benefits%20from%20the%20government%3A%20Megha%20Engineering%20%26amp%3B%20Infra%20has%20given%20over%20Rs.%20800%20crores%20in%20EBs.%20In%20April%202023%2C%20they%20donated%20Rs.%20140%20crore%2C%20and%20just%20one%20month%20later%2C%20they%20were%20awarded%20the%20Rs.%2014%2C400%20crore%20Thane-Borivali%20Twin%20Tunnel%20Project%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJindal%20Steel%20and%20Power%20gave%20Rs.%2025%20crore%20in%20EBs%20on%207%20October%202022%2C%20and%20just%20three%20days%20later%2C%20they%20won%20the%20Gare%20Palma%20IV%2F6%20coal%20mine%2C%20on%2010th%20October%202022%2C%20Mr%20Ramesh%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHafta%20Vasooli%3A%20The%20BJP's%20Hafta%20Vasooli%20strategy%20is%20simple%20raid%20a%20target%20through%20the%20ED%2FCBI%2FIT%2C%20and%20then%20seek%20hafta%20(%26quot%3Bdonations%26quot%3B)%20for%20the%20company's%20protection.%20At%20least%2014%20of%20the%20top%2030%20donors%20have%20been%20raided%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%20an%20investigation%20found%20that%20after%20ED%2FCBI%2FIT%20raids%2C%20companies%20were%20forced%20to%20donate%20to%20the%20BJP%20via%20electoral%20trusts%2C%20Ramesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20same%20companies%20have%20donated%20through%20EBs%2C%20like%20Hetero%20Pharma%20and%20Yashoda%20Hospital%2C%20he%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20IT%20department%20raided%20Shirdi%20Sai%20Electricals%20in%20December%202023%2C%20and%20in%20January%202024%2C%20they%20donated%20Rs.%2040%20crore%20through%20Electoral%20Bonds%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20leader%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFuture%20Gaming%20%26amp%3B%20Hotels%2C%20has%20donated%20over%20Rs%201200%20crore%2C%20making%20it%20the%20largest%20donor%20in%20the%20data%20so%20far.%20Here%20is%20the%20chronology%3A%20April%202%202022%3A%20ED%20raids%20Future%2C%20and%205%20days%20later%20(7th%20April)%20they%20donate%20Rs.%20100%20crores%20in%20EBs%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramesh%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIT%20department%20raids%20Future%20in%20October%202023%20and%20the%20same%20month%20they%20donate%20Rs.%2065%20crores%20in%20EBs%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramesh%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20data%20also%20points%20to%20kickbacks%20as%20a%20pattern%20emerges%20where%20immediately%20after%20receiving%20some%20handouts%20from%20the%20Central%20government%2C%20companies%20have%20repaid%20the%20favour%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVedanta%20got%20the%20Radhikapur%20West%20private%20coal%20mine%20on%203rd%20March%202021%2C%20and%20then%20in%20April%202021%2C%20they%20donated%20Rs.%2025%20crore%20in%20Electoral%20Bonds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMegha%20Engineering%20%26amp%3B%20Infra%20got%20the%20Rs.%204%2C500%20crore%20Zojila%20tunnel%20project%20in%20August%202020%2C%20then%20donated%20Rs.%2020%20crore%20in%20Electoral%20Bonds%20in%20October%202020%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20claimed%20that%20Megha%20got%20the%20BKC%20bullet%20train%20station%20contract%20in%20December%202022%2C%20and%20donated%20Rs.%2056%20crore%20the%20same%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramesh%20alleged%20that%20data%20also%20shows%20there%20has%20been%20money%20laundering%20through%20shell%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20huge%20issue%20with%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20is%20that%20it%20removed%20the%20restriction%20that%20only%20a%20small%20percentage%20of%20a%20company's%20profits%20could%20be%20donated%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20shell%20companies%20to%20donate%20black%20money.%20There%20are%20many%20such%20suspicious%20cases%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Rs.%20410%20crore%20that%20has%20been%20donated%20by%20Qwik%20Supply%20Chain%20Limited%2C%20a%20company%20whose%20entire%20share%20capital%20is%20just%20Rs.%20130%20crores%20according%20to%20MoCA%20filings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20said%20another%20major%20issue%20is%20missing%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20provided%20by%20SBI%20only%20begins%20in%20April%202019%2C%20but%20SBI%20sold%20the%20first%20tranche%20of%20bonds%20in%20March%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20total%20of%20Rs.%202%2C500%20crores%20in%20bonds%20are%20missing%20from%20this%20data.%20Where%20is%20the%20data%20of%20these%20missing%20bonds%2C%20from%20March%202018%20to%20April%202019%3F%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20the%20very%20first%20tranche%20of%20bonds%2C%20the%20BJP%20bagged%2095%25%20of%20the%20funds.%20Who%20is%20the%20BJP%20trying%20to%20protect%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20analysis%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20data%20continues%2C%20many%20more%20such%20cases%20of%20the%20BJP's%20corruption%20will%20become%20clear.%20We%20also%20continue%20to%20demand%20unique%20bond%20ID%20numbers%2C%20so%20that%20we%20can%20precisely%20match%20donors%20to%20recipients%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramesh%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20data%20points%20to%20kickbacks%20as%20a%20pattern%20emerges%20where%20immediately%20after%20receiving%20some%20handouts%20from%20the%20Central%20government%2C%20companies%20have%20repaid%20the%20favour%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%20From%20steel%20tycoon%20Lakshmi%20Mittal%20to%20billionaire%20Sunil%20Bharti%20Mittal's%20Airtel%2C%20Anil%20Agarwal's%20Vedanta%2C%20ITC%2C%20Mahindra%20and%20Mahindra%2C%20and%20a%20lesser-known%20Future%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%20were%20among%20the%20prominent%20buyers%20of%20the%20now-scrapped%20electoral%20bonds%20for%20making%20political%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20directive%2C%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%2C%20which%20was%20the%20authorised%20seller%20of%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20shared%20the%20data%20with%20the%20poll%20panel%20on%20March%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20given%20the%20Election%20Commission%20time%20till%205%20pm%20on%20March%2015%20to%20upload%20the%20data%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SBI%20said%20a%20total%20of%2022%2C217%20electoral%20bonds%20of%20varying%20denominations%20were%20purchased%20by%20donors%20between%20April%201%2C%202019%2C%20and%20February%2015%20this%20year%2C%20out%20of%20which%2022%2C030%20were%20redeemed%20by%20political%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710479340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Flpdlvpmg_jairam-ramesh_625x300_15_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-says-electoral-bonds-data-exposes-bjps-corrupt-tactics-5241950%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20on%20Friday%20alleged%20that%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20data%20has%20exposed%20%26quot%3Bcorrupt%20tactics%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20BJP%20such%20as%20quid%20pro%20quo%2C%20seeking%20donations%20for%20the%20company's%20protection%2C%20kickbacks%20and%20money%20laundering%20through%20shell%20companies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-says-electoral-bonds