for%20Putin%2C%20merely%20winning%20has%20never%20been%20enough%20%E2%80%94%20and%202024%20looks%20no%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPutin%20needs%20to%20show%20that%20Russians%20really%20want%20him%20to%20lead%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Putin%2C%20it's%20not%20about%20winning.%20It's%20about%20winning%20big.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20Thomas%20Graham%2C%20a%20fellow%20at%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfr.org%2Fexpert-brief%2Fwhy-russias-election-matters-putin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECouncil%20on%20Foreign%20Relations%2C%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrote%20on%20March%207%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%26quot%3BJust%20winning%20has%20never%20been%20enough%20for%20Putin.%20He%20must%20win%20in%20a%20fashion%20that%20demonstrates%20that%20he%20remains%20the%20master%20of%20the%20Russian%20political%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Szakonyi%2C%20a%20political-science%20professor%20at%20George%20Washington%20University%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Russian%20authorities%20placed%20so%20much%20emphasis%20on%20voter%20turnout%20rates%20for%20the%20election%20that%20state-linked%20employers%20would%20pressure%20their%20employees%20to%20show%20up%20at%20the%20ballot%20boxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESzakonyi%2C%20who's%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20sponsored%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-64911-20%26h%3D475f26c5df082792371de5350bda738415a028e68a7931dcb0cbb4875ef3676e%26postID%3D65f1206148eec3d3e787c683%26postSlug%3Drussia-economy-presidential-election-putin-just-winning-not-enough-2024-3%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FPolitics-Profit-Elections-Policymaking-Comparative%252Fdp%252F1108491634%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EPolitics%20for%20Profit%3A%20Business%2C%20Elections%2C%20and%20Policymaking%20in%20Russia%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20that%2