20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1768289000765132923%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20left%20to%20the%20visiting%20Bhutanese%20leader%20to%20announce%20that%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20had%20%E2%80%9Cagreed%20to%20visit%20Bhutan%20soon%E2%80%A6%20next%20week%2C%20in%20fact!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWonderful%20to%20meet%20my%20friend%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Shri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40narendramodi%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20thanked%20him%20for%20his%20steadfast%20support%20to%20Bhutan%2C%20and%20we%20discussed%20a%20range%20of%20issues%20to%20strengthen%20relations%20between%20Bhutan%20and%20India.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20Ji%20also%20agreed%20to%20visit%20Bhutan%20soon%20%E2%80%A6%20next%20week%2C%20in%20fact!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F7yWIxyWbWn%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F7yWIxyWbWn%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Tshering%20Tobgay%20(%40tsheringtobgay)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftsheringtobgay%2Fstatus%2F1768331914098905502%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Bhutan%20has%20consistently%20topped%20the%20list%20as%20the%20largest%20recipient%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20development%20aid%20budget%2C%20with%20India%20serving%20as%20its%20principal%20trade%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20relationship%20may%20be%20evolving%20as%20Thimpu%20has%20accelerated%20talks%20with%20China%20on%20resolving%20its%20disputed%20boundary%20since%202021.%20Once%20Bhutan%20fully%20demarcates%20its%20border%20with%20China%2C%20that%20will%20likely%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20full%20diplomatic%20ti