2C%20I%20spotted%20veteran%20farmer%20leader%20Yudhvir%20Singh%20(BKU%20Tikait)%20and%20asked%20him%20about%20the%20status%20of%20SKM%20(non-political).%20%E2%80%9COnly%20two%20leaders%20from%20SKM%20have%20opened%20a%20camp%20at%20the%20border.%20We%20support%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20question%20of%20disunity%20still%20lingered.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20one%20person%20goes%20away%20from%20SKM%2C%20it%20means%20one%20less%20voice%20in%20our%20fight%20for%20MSP%20%5Bminimum%20support%20price%5D.%20All%20farmers%20should%20come%20together.%20With%20unity%20we%20got%20the%20three%20farm%20laws%20taken%20back%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99ll%20be%20unity%20that%20secures%20MSP%20for%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20nearly%20midday%2C%20the%20crowds%20had%20swelled%20between%2040%2C000%20and%2050%2C000%20farmers.%20I%20spoke%20to%20a%20farmer%20from%20Sonepat%2C%20Rajesh%20Dahiya%2C%20who%20said%20that%20more%20people%20would%20have%20come%20if%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20had%20not%20put%20blockades%20and%20caused%20traffic%20jams.%20He%20added%20that%20around%20100%20people%20had%20come%20from%20his%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavi%2C%20a%20middle-aged%20farmer%20from%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Karnal%2C%20said%20he%20grows%20sugarcane%2C%20chana%2C%20and%20raises%20milk-producing%20animals%20like%20buffaloes%20and%20cows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSugarcane%20farmers%20are%20burdened%20with%20debt%20and%20no%20government%20has%20been%20able%20to%20solve%20our%20problem.%20Today%2C%20my%20family%20survives%20because%20I%20sell%20milk.%20We%20are%20in%20debt%20because%20of%20growing%20cash%20crops.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20even%20imagine%20the%20fate%20of%20farmers%20who%20grow%20non-cash%20crops%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F14194804%2Fimage15.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F14194804%2Fimage15.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F14194804%2Fimage15-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F14194804%2Fimage15-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701687%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKisan%20mahapanchayat%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20on%20March%2014.%20Photo%3A%20Indra%20Shekhar%20Singh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Why%20is%20the%20government%20going%20back%20on%20its%20MSP%20promise%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20caught%20up%20with%20Bimla%20Devi%20from%20rural%20Rewa%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20a%20Left%20farmers%E2%80%99%20union%20and%20travelled%20all%20the%20way%20with%2015%20women%2C%20demanding%20their%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20I%20used%20to%20grow%20vegetables%20and%20food%20in%20my%20own%201%20acre%20family%20farm.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20debt%2C%20my%20husband%20lost%20the%20farm.%20Now%20my%20son%2C%20husband%20and%20I%20work%20on%20other%20people%E2%80%99s%20farms.%20If%20there%20was%20an%20MSP%20guarantee%20for%20our%20crops%2C%20we%20would%20have%20never%20fallen%20into%20debt.%20All%20these%20women%20with%20me%20share%20the%20same%20story.%20We%20want%20to%20know%20why%20the%20government%20is%20going%20back%20on%20its%20promise%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20was%20heating%20up%2C%20and%20with%20limited%20water%20supply%2C%20the%20heat%20was%20getting%20unbearable.%20Yet%2C%20the%20farmers%20continued%20to%20cheer%20their%20leaders%20as%20they%20were%20up%20on%20stage.%20Prominent%20leaders%20like%20Joginder%20Singh%20Ugrahan%2C%20Darshan%20Pal%2C%20Hannan%20Mollah%2C%20Rakesh%20Tikait%2C%20among%20others%20were%20sitting%20on%20a%20canopy-less%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F14194706%2Fimage24.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F14194706%2Fimage24.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F14194706%2Fimage24-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F14194706%2Fimage24-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701686%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKisan%20mahapanchayat%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20on%20March%2014.%20Photo%3A%20Indra%20Shekhar%20Singh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20I%20spoke%20with%20B.%20Nagendra%2C%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20minister%20for%20youth%20empowerment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20misconception%20that%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%20is%20not%20flourishing%20in%20Karnataka%20or%20the%20South.%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20in%20Karnataka%20is%20the%20victory%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement.%20We%2C%20the%20farmers%2C%20have%20been%20organising%20%5Bprotests%5D%20since%20the%20%5BCOVID-19%5D%20lockdown%2C%20and%20it%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20farmers%2C%20Dalits%20groups%2C%20working%20class%2C%20and%20labourers%20have%20all%20joined%20together%20against%20injustices%20done%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20state%20such%20as%20land%20ceiling%20reformation%20and%20other%20ordinances.%20We%20started%20the%20movement%20even%20before%20%5Bthe%5D%20Delhi%20%5Bprotest%5D%20and%2042%20organisations%20led%20this%20effort%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20now%2C%20Rakesh%20Tikait%20had%20taken%20the%20stage%2C%20and%20the%20crowd%20was%20ecstatic%20despite%20the%20heat.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20government%20is%20lying%20alright.%20They%20stopped%20talking%20with%20us%2C%20and%20then%20they%20turned%20around%20and%20blamed%20us%20for%20the%20breakdown%20in%20negotiations.%20When%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20want%20to%20talk%20to%20us%2C%20how%20will%20they%20resolve%20the%20MSP%20issue%3F%20Today%2C%20there%20are%20several%20movements%20happening%20simultaneously%20in%20the%20country.%20But%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20the%20Andolan%20(movement)%20of%20Bihar%20or%20Karnataka%20or%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20Delhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20got%20down%20from%20the%20stage%2C%20I%20spoke%20with%20him.%20In%20a%20candid%20conversation%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20government%20is%20run%20by%20a%20gang%20of%20corporates%20who%20are%20controlling%20the%20BJP%20and%20this%20country.%20They%20are%20after%20our%20lands%20and%20our%20food.%20Once%20they%20are%20in%20control%20of%20agriculture%2C%20we%20will%20be%20enslaved%20again%20by%20a%20new%20company%20raj.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20spoke%20with%20social%20activist%20Medha%20Patkar%2C%20who%20clearly%20pointed%20out%20the%20threats%20to%20Indian%20agriculture%20posed%20by%20%E2%80%9Ccorporates%20and%20Bill%20Gates.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20stressed%20on%20the%20loss%20of%20biodiversity%20and%20destruction%20of%20indigenous%20systems%20of%20agriculture%20under%20corporate%20pressure.%20She%20advocated%20for%20regenerative%20or%20organic%20agriculture%20as%20a%20potential%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20now%20past%201%20pm%2C%20and%20it%20was%20evident%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3Emahapanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20dominated%20by%20three%20factions%3A%20BKU%20Tikait%2C%20Ugrahan%2C%20and%20the%20combined%20Left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20spoke%20with%20Joginder%20Singh%20Ugrahan%20for%20the%20last%20word%20and%20achievements%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Emahapanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20big%20achievement%20for%20us%2C%20as%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20will%20be%20active%20soon.%20It%E2%80%99s%20been%20two%20years%20since%20the%20laws%20were%20rescinded.%20We%20have%20conducted%20numerous%20programmes%2C%20yet%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20not%20been%20listening.%20They%20never%20wanted%20to%20talk%20with%20us.%20This%20is%20our%20way%20of%20exposing%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20the%20public%20and%20let%20them%20decide%20whether%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20a%20friend%20or%20an%20enemy%20of%20the%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20sowing%20dissent%20among%20the%20people.%20While%20they%20are%20doing%20a%20good%20job%2C%20however%2C%20we%20have%20to%20work%20around%20it%20%5Baddress%20these%20challenges%20together%5D.%20That%20is%20why%20we%20have%20proposed%20a%20minimum%20work%20programme%20through%20which%20both%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20groups%20can%20come%20together%20and%20fight%20this%20issue%20as%20one%20%5Ba%20united%20force%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710469816000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F14194344%2Fimage-1957.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fif-there-was-an-msp-guarantee-wed-have-never-fallen-into-debt-farmers-at-kisan-mahapanchayat%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Sugarcane%20farmers%20are%20burdened%20with%20debt%20and%20no%20government%20has%20been%20able%20to%20solve%20our%20problem.%20Today%2C%20my%20family%20survives%20because%20I%20sell%20milk.%20We%20are%20in%20debt%20because%20of%20growing%20cash%20crops.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20even%20imagine%20the%20fate%20of%20farmers%20who%20grow%20non-cash%20crops%2C'%20said%20a%20farmer%20from%20Haryana's%20Karnal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22c