20a%20datewise%20list%20of%20purchases%20by%20companies%2C%20and%20the%20other%20a%20datewise%20list%20of%20deposits%20by%20political%20parties%20that%20have%20encashed%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFuture%20Gaming%3A%20Under%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20lens%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFuture%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%20PR%20has%20donated%20Rs%201%2C368%20crore%20between%20October%2021%2C%202020%20and%20January%209%2C%202024%2C%20all%20in%20denominations%20of%20Rs%201%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoimbatore-based%20Future%20Gaming%20is%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20lottery%20companies%20and%20its%20founder%20Santiago%20Martin%2C%20styles%20himself%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Clottery%20king.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2023%2C%202019%2C%20the%20ED%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchennai%2Fed-attaches-rs-120-crore-assets-of-martin-in-tamil-nadu-lottery-scam%2Farticleshow%2F70338379.cms%5C%22%3E%20attached%20assets%20worth%20Rs%20120%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20scam%2C%20where%20he%20was%20accused%20of%20inflating%20prize%20money%20and%20amassing%20property%20from%20unaccounted%20cash%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20said%20that%20a%20few%20months%20earlier%2C%20the%20ED%20had%20searched%20over%2070%20premises%20associated%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20data%20now%20made%20available%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20the%20company%20proceeded%20to%20purchase%20electoral%20bonds%20after%20this%20action%2C%20with%20its%20first%20purchase%20being%20listed%20on%20October%2021%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20company%20has%20remained%20under%20the%20lens%20of%20the%20ED%2C%20with%20the%20agency%20conducting%20searches%20in%20its%20premises%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20as%20recently%20as%20last%20week%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20sand%20mining%20case%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20%3Cem%3EPress%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%202%2C%202022%2C%20it%20was%20reported%20that%20the%20ED%20had%20initiated%20a%20money%20laundering%20probe%20against%20the%20company%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fed-money-laundering-case-future-gaming-rs-409-crore-assets-1932708-2022-04-02%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseized%20Rs%20409.92%20crore%20worth%20of%20its%20assets%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Five%20days%20later%2C%20on%20April%207%2C%202022%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20data%2C%20the%20company%20bought%20around%20Rs%20100%20crore%20worth%20of%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202022%2C%20election%20watchdog%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fadrindia.org%2Fcontent%2Flottery-company-future-gaming-highest-donor-electoral-trust%5C%22%3E%20analysed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Contribution%20Reports%20of%20Electoral%20Trusts%20submitted%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20for%20FY%202020-21%20and%20noted%20that%20the%20lottery%20company%20had%20donated%20Rs%20100%20crore%20to%20Prudent%20Electoral%20Trust%2C%20which%20has%20donated%20the%20highest%20amount%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20would%20raided%20companies%20ever%20go%20about%20making%20political%20contributions%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20raids%2C%20if%20not%20as%20protection%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farun_srikumar%2Fstatus%2F1768335436441882898%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etweeted%20Arun%20Srikumar%2C%20a%20lawyer%20at%20Keystone%20Partners%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20adding%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Czero%20bona%20fides%20in%20these%20contributions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20total%20number%20of%20electoral%20bonds